                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"c1\">Bij het evaluatiegesprek kunt u gebruik maken van de competentietabel m.b.t. praktische vaardigheden (klik het bovenstaande symbool  aan om het bestand te openen) of het onderstaande overzicht (klik het onderstaande symbool aan om het bestand te openen). Zorg ervoor dat elke onderdeel even aan de orde komt</span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span class=\"c1\"> </span></strong><strong><span class=\"c1\"> </span></strong><strong><span class=\"c1\">Beoordelingsmatrix</span></strong><strong><span class=\"c1\"> </span></strong><strong><span class=\"c1\"> </span></strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"MsoNormalTable\" align=\"left\">\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"height-21.5pt\">\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"559\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-419.5pt height-21.5pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span class=\"font-size-14pt\">Samenwerken en communicatieve competenties</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-21.5pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-21.5pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-16pt\">competenties</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-21.5pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-16pt\">Opmerkingen</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-21.5pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-21.5pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">sociaal gevoel, betrokkenheid verantwoordelijkheid nemen</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-21.5pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-17pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">Flexibiliteit</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-17pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">Omgang met klasgenoten</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-17pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">Omgang met docenten, schoolleiding</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-17pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">Gesprek voeren: correct spreken, Luisteren, begrijpen</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-17pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">Begrijpend Lezen.</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-21.5pt\">\n<td colspan=\"2\" width=\"559\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-419.5pt height-21.5pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p alig