 width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-17pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">Persoonlijke verzorging</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-17pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">Reflectie op eigen handelen</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-17pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"height-19.85pt\">\n<td width=\"370\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-277.25pt height-19.85pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span class=\"font-size-12pt\">Open staan voor veranderingen</span></p>\n</td>\n<td width=\"190\" valign=\"top\" class=\"width-142.25pt height-19.85pt\" style=\"background-color:transparent;\">\n<p align=\"left\"> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span class=\"c1\"> </span></strong><span class=\"font-size-12pt\"> </span><span class=\"font-size-12pt\"> </span><strong><span class=\"c1\"> </span></strong><span class=\"c1\"> </span><strong><span class=\"c1\"> </span></strong><span class=\"c2\"> </span></p>\n"
